            </row>
            <row>
              <entry><emphasis effect="bold">Orientation with Regard to the World of Work</emphasis>The learner will be able to make informed decisions about further study and career choices.</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>
                <emphasis effect="italics">We know this when the learner:</emphasis>
              </entry>
            </row>
            <row>
              <entry>5.1 identifies and discusses career and study choices and their corresponding requirements;</entry>
            </row>
            <row>
